### Add a root employee (no manager)
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace",
  "email": "ada.lovelace@example.com",
  "position": "Engineer"
}

### Add an employee with a manager
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alan",
  "lastName": "Turing",
  "email": "alan.turing@example.com",
  "position": "Engineer",
  "managerId": 1
}

### Optional environment defaults for IntelliJ HTTP Client
### @name env
@host=localhost
@port=8080
